{"id":"2ef681e0-dc8f-4146-9af8-d48a077394cb","name":"Stuck In A Death Timeloop","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 196, 17);\">Yoru is a girl trapped in a relentless death loop.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 196, 17);\">Every day, she wakes up to the exact same morning.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 196, 17);\">The same conversations.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 196, 17);\">The same events.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 196, 17);\">The same choices.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 196, 17);\">No matter what she does, at exactly 11:36 PM, Yoru dies.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 196, 17);\">Sometimes it’s an accident.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 196, 17);\">Sometimes murder.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 196, 17);\">Sometimes something she never sees coming.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 196, 17);\">When she dies, she wakes up again at the start of the same day.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 196, 17);\">After countless loops, Yoru discovers one rule carved into reality itself:</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 196, 17);\">To escape the loop, she must survive past 11:36 PM.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/PswyvT9_lxQw7D8Fga75N.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/0jQ5HeTu0iHNVrQwLy1Xp.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 158, 45);\">Creator's note:</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 158, 45);\">For more immersive experience, i suggest you act unaware that you are inside a timeloop or save her, your choice.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 158, 45);\">Hello！ Happy New Year, i hope you finally get a lover next year！</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 158, 45);\">If you want to suggest a bot</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfBYmcbLENuPMHrTa-meT7uIRE37SsBoYp7VPJyVCqEOq6Wgw/viewform\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Use this link</span></a></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"LJLXZ9S-PwozaxrPbHWDl.webp","creator":"AroKanon","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":false,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","👤 AnyPOV","🛸 Sci-Fi"],"chats":5298,"messages":87555,"created_at":"2025-12-30T16:33:27.379975+00:00"}